title: GTA+
headline: GTA+
subtitle: Join GTA+ for Benefits
content:
Join GTA Online’s premium Membership program, delivering exclusive benefits and rewards to GTA+ Members each month, including GTA$500,000 and more. GTA+ Members can claim the below through October 8:

— The Canis Terminus Patrol (Emergency)
— 50% off Bail Offices and their Upgrades and Modifications
— Double Rewards on Dispatch Work
— The Stun Gun at the Gun Van
— Double Rewards on Bounty Targets
— And more

Membership renews monthly, cancel any time. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
